Subject: [PATCH] spi: atmel-quadspi: Create `atmel_qspi_ops` to support newer
 SoC families
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1012628
